Y A sh S ANJY o T   A INAPURE  ainapureyash2@gmail.com   7028925507   portfolio   linkedin   github  Ed UCATION  D.Y.Patil College of Engineering and Technology   Kolhapur  B.Tech Computer Science   GPA: 7.4   August 2023 - Present  D.Y.Patil Polytechnic   Kolhapur  Diploma Computer Science   GPA: 9   August 2020 - June 2023  Ex PERIENCE  SIBIC Incubation Center  Frontend Developer - Intern   Jun 2024 - Dec 2024     Worked on an IMS software project for SIBIC using React, Redux, Spring Boot, and MySQL. Collaborated with UI designers and backend developers to build a responsive frontend. Used Redux for efficient state management, enabling seamless handling of large data sets.  GSP Technologies  Frontend Developer - Intern   Jan 2025 - Jun 2025     Built a fully responsive hotel website using React.js, with booking system, payment integration, and admin panel. Collaborated with the backend team (Spring Boot) & design team to deliver a production-ready application.  GSSOC  Maintainer   Nov 2024 - Dec 2024     I Worked as a repository maintainer where I reviewed the PR's and merged them and maintained the repository on github.The repository has over 30 contributors.  Sk ILLS  Framework/Libraries:   Reactjs, Nextjs, Expressjs, Nodejs, Tailwind, Zod, Aceternity Database:   MongoDB, PostgreSQL, MySqI, MariaDB  Tools:   Postman, Git, Linux  Platforms:   GitHub, Cloudnary, Vercel  Languages:   Java, Javascript, Typescript, Python  P RO j ECTS  DYPCET-Chatbot -   Nextjs, lamma ai, typescript, tailwind css, mysql   Link       Developed an agentic chatbot integrated with a MySQL database to automate student queries.     Implemented natural language understanding for user interactions and created backend tools to fetch  real-time data. The system efficiently handles tasks such as retrieving attendance and timetables through conversational inputs, improving user accessibility and reducing manual workload  Voyago: Android Application -   Java , Firebase   Developed a MakeMyTrip-like travel app with features such as browsing destinations, booking trips, payment gateway integration, and user authentication.   Collaborated with a teammate, gaining experience in managing large-scale databases and improving teamwork skills.  DYPCETClubs -   React, Typescript, Aceternity UI, Tailwind css, Groq api   Link       Build a responsive web app for efficient college club management. It enables club leaders to register clubs, manage events, post announcements, handle memberships, and create AI-powered quizzes.  Ac HIEVEMENTS  Codepeak '23     secured the top 10th rank in the CODEPEAK 2023 Open Source Contribution Event, hosted by IIT Patna and IIT Guwahati.  Hackathons     1st rank in Pratham Code hackathon - june 2024     1st rank in InnovateX Hackathon - Dec 2024     Ranked top 5 among 60+ teams during an 48 hour national-level hackathon hosted by Sanjay Ghodawat Institute.  Certifications   Github Foundations -   Github   Database Structures and Management with MySQL -   Coursera
